      <title>加拿大将外国人购房禁令延长至 2026 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/canada-extends-ban-on-home-purchases-by-foreigners-through-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着房地产市场开始出现反弹迹象，加拿大将针对外国购房者的禁令又延长了两年，引发了人们对多伦多和温哥华等城市住房成本的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/canada-extends-ban-on-home-purchases-by-foreigners-through-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 18:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着银行改革的开始，澳洲联储将利率维持在 12 年高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/rba-set-to-hold-rate-at-12-year-high-as-bank-overhaul-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人们普遍预计澳大利亚央行将在今年的第一次会议上将利率维持在 12 年来的高位，投资者将目光集中在经过修改的沟通制度下的未来政策路径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/rba-set-to-hold-rate-at-12-year-high-as-bank-overhaul-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普若当选将对中国商品征收超过60%的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/trump-floats-chinese-goods-tariff-of-more-than-60-if-elected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，如果当选，他可能对中国商品征收超过60%的关税，这表明对美国最大商品供应商的态度越来越强硬。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/trump-floats-chinese-goods-tariff-of-more-than-60-if-elected</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 17:19:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
