      <title>德意志银行预计在新行长的领导下土耳其将再次加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/deutsche-bank-sees-another-turkey-hike-under-new-governor-s-helm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行表示，土耳其央行行长的更替和通胀的加剧为进一步加息开辟了空间，而前行长哈菲兹·盖伊·埃尔坎领导下的土耳其银行曾表示，加息将于 1 月份结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/deutsche-bank-sees-another-turkey-hike-under-new-governor-s-helm</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 16:17:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
